# Royal Swag Design System

Primary app: `E:\projects\Royal swag\old royal swag`. Read `DESIGN_SYSTEM.md` and `.cursor/rules/royal-swag-design-system.mdc` there.

## Quick reference

- **Colors:** `--primary` #324023, `--gold` #9A6F1A, `--parchment` #F4EDD6, glass tokens in `globals.css`
- **Fonts:** Playfair Display (headlines), Hanken Grotesk (body)
- **Utilities:** `.glass-card`, `.btn-primary`, `font-display`, `font-body`
- **Logo:** `/public/images/royal-swag-logo.png` — `<BrandLogo variant="on-dark|on-light" header />`, min 40px in header

## Do not change without client approval

- Tagline: "Breathe Clean. Live Free."
- Free Lung Test, 30-Day Guarantee badge
- Herb names/copy: Tulsi, Vasaka, Mulethi, Pippali
- Prices
